plot: Dennis, Mac, and Dee take part in the Philadelphia Eagles' open tryouts, while Frank drops acid and freaks out when he and Charlie tailgate next to the McPoyles.

When the Philadelphia Eagles have open tryouts, Dennis, Mac, and Dee all try out. And while watching the tryouts, Frank and Charlie find out that the Mcpoyles are there too. Being that Frank needs to use the restroom, he must use the Mcboyles bathroom but first needs to take some of their milk to get in, which seems not to be only milk.—James Hake
